Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:04.31,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,By the decision of Ying Zheng, the king that wished to unite all of China,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:04.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N天下統一の道を行く王 嬴政(えいせい)のもと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:07.10,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the State of Qin began its invasion of the State of Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国(しんこく)は 魏国(ぎこく)へと侵攻した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:11.48,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The enemy blocking their way is the legendary Great General, Lian Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:11.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ちはだかる敵は\N伝説の大将軍 廉頗(れんぱ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:17.74,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Young generals take on this relentless battlefield in hopes of rendering great military achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,若き将たちは 大いなる武功を狙い\Nこの苛烈な戦場に挑む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:26.00,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,One night after the Feixin Unit, Yufeng Unit, and Yuehua Unit launched their attack on Lun Hu's headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信(ひしん)隊 玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊 楽華(がくか)隊による\N輪虎(りんこ)本陣急襲から一夜明け…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水(そすい)）信どの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.86,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Lord Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nハハハッ… さすがに見えねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.76,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Guess he can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）戦いの中心で\N命を懸けている男たちは―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:45.38,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,And at the center of all of this, the men risking their lives in battle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不思議なことに察していた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.98,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,sensed something mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁(もうごう)）フッ… やはり そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.28,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:01:00.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）これから 山陽(さんよう)大攻略戦\Nその最後の日の 幕が開けることを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:01:00.63,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,The curtain now opens on the final day of the war to capture Shanyang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.66,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Whadda ya mean we're in the rear reserve unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:09.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが後方予備隊って\Nどういうことだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:13.98,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,What do you expect after acting on your own so much yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（栄備(えいび)）昨日 あれだけ\N勝手をしておいて 当然じゃろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンンッ… あと 何じゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.17,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,And what's with that attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:24.80,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,The Yuehua, Yufeng, and Feixin Units will all be getting along here as a rear reserve unit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その口の利き方は\N（殴る音）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:24.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（栄備）楽華 玉鳳 飛信３隊は\N今日は 仲良く後方配備だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.70,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Rear... unit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）後ろ …ですか\N（尾平(びへい)）やっぱ そうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.81,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Yeah, makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:33.81,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But General, what about the morale\N we worked so hard to raise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:33.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど 将軍\Nこれじゃ せっかく上がった士気が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… まあ そう ぼやくな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.07,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,Quit complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.91,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,Lun Hu will probably come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:41.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく また輪虎は出てくる\Nそれなら お前たちにとっては―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.24,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,When that happens, being a reserve unit won't be such a bad deal for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,予備隊も悪くなかろうが\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）将軍の\Nおっしゃるとおりです 信どの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:47.54,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,The general is correct, Lord Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）陣の前方に組み込まれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.02,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,If he cuts into the formation from the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運よく そこに輪虎が\N攻めてこなければ 出会えませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:56.44,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,unless you're lucky enough to be the unit Lun Hu attacks, you won't encounter him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:59.66,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,But if you're a reserve unit that is covering a wide range,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:59.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 持ち場の\N広い後方予備隊なら―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつでも対応できる\N（信）ああ そっか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.45,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,you can adapt to any situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.72,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So basically, general, you're giving us permission to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは 将軍は俺たちに輪虎を…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:11.73,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,Normally, you'd be torn limb from limb for violating military laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来ならば 軍律違反で\N八つ裂きにすべき お前らだが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… まあ\Nあの輪虎の本陣を突いた その力は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:16.52,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,But seeing as you managed to penetrate Lun Hu's headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも土門(どもん)も本物だと評価している
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.11,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,both Tu Men and I have judged your ability to be genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:23.31,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,So don't blunder next time, Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は しくじるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！\N（信）ウッ！ ゴホッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:32.22,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,So until that opportunity arises, you can just stare at my ass from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:31.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では その機が来るまで\N後ろで わしのケツでも眺めておれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（栄備）今朝の雲は厚いなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.64,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,We've got some thick clouds today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は荒れそうじゃのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.11,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be a stormy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:04.36,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.25\c&H000000&\pos(638,101.667)}The Hour of Conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）流尹(るい)平野の戦い ６日目\N蒙驁は 従来どおり―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.61,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Day 6 of the battle on the Liuyin Plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:13.79,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,As he has up until this point, Meng Ao has positioned horizontal units as the main defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:16.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,横陣(おうじん)という守備主体の構えを敷いて\N魏国軍を迎え撃つ態勢だった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.72,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and has prepared for an attack on the State of Wei Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:20.38,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,At the right wing is General Tu Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右翼には土門将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左翼には栄備将軍を配し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.34,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And stationed on the left wing is General Rong Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:28.39,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,At the rear of the right wing is the Yuehua Unit and the Yufeng Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:27.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右翼後方に楽華隊 玉鳳隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:32.70,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Behind the left wing is the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左翼後方には飛信隊が予備隊として\Nそれぞれの持ち場に就いている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.14,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,All three as reserve units ready at their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:41.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 中央軍後方の高台には\N蒙驁の本陣があり―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:42.16,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And on the high ground behind the central army is Meng Ao's headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:44.77,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,where he surveyed over the Liuyin Plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流尹平野を見渡していた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）\N介子坊(かいしぼう)さんの補充兵は まだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.89,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Are the reserve soldiers from Jie Zifang here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎兵）まだです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Not yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失った僕の兵は介子坊の兵で埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:20.08,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,I will fill in my lost soldiers with Jie Zifang's. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 重量級の彼らが―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:25.07,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,But I wonder how well those heavyweight-class soldiers will be able to keep up with my fighting style. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の戦い方に\Nどこまで ついてこられるか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:29.76,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Though the State of Wei soldiers are the same on that point. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最も その点に関しては\N魏国兵も同じだけれども
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:36.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏良(ぎりょう)）\N輪虎将軍 貴殿は勘違いされておる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You are mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 廉頗将軍をはじめとする\Nあなた方の復帰戦にあらず
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:41.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This is not your nor General Lian Po's comeback war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:47.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 秦国の犬どもの侵略から\N国を守る我々 魏国人の戦いだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:47.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This is our, the citizens of the State of Wei's war to defend our land from those State of Qin dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:52.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Everyone is here to protect their country and their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:52.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みな国を\N家族を守るために 戦いに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その思いを その命を―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:59.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We are entrusting all of those feelings and lives to you in these battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全て あなたに預けて戦うのだ！\N（輪虎）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:07.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Please, put a bit more trust in our abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:06.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと我々の力を信用してくだされ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々が\N将軍の兵の力に及ばないのなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.61,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,And if our power is not as great as that of your soldiers, General,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:16.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,we will make up for what we lack with emotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足りない分は\N気持ちで埋めてみせまする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.72,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Good. We should be amply able to fight with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし… これは これで 十分 戦える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:38.27,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,We'll start without waiting for Jie Zifang's soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,介子坊の兵を待たずに始めるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.14,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Your name is Wei Liang, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏良 …だったね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.24,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:48.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日 狙うのは 敵中央軍の\N後ろにいる総大将 蒙驁の首だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:48.65,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,Today, our target is the head of Supreme Commander Meng Ao, located at the back of the enemy central army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:53.16,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I need everyone to fight with the fury of desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなには\N死にものぐるいで働いてもらうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:05.13,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,It looks like those State of Wei soldiers suddenly had a boost in morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）魏国のヤツら\N急に士気が上がりましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.51,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you make of this, Lord Meng Tian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（じい）蒙恬(もうてん)さま こ… これは…\N（蒙恬）やるね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.63,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.78,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,I suppose today really is going to be the critical moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 今日が本番ですね\N（信）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:13.63,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.18,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Come at me, Lun Hu! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来い 輪虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:25.19,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,All units, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（輪虎）全軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）\N殺せ！ 秦国の犬どもを殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill the State of Qin dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:55.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）前衛の全てが\N猛攻を受けているようです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:55.47,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Everyone in the vanguard are meeting with a fierce attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.10,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuan, can you see Lun Hu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渕さん 輪虎は見えるか？\N（渕）ここからでは何とも…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.97,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:04.12,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,Though we may have a large station in the rear,  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後方で 持ち場が広いとはいえ\Nやはり輪虎と当たるかは運しだいか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.16,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,hitting Lun Hu is still going to depend a lot on luck. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy army has the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）敵軍の力が偏っている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎は右にいるもようです！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.24,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lun Hu seems to be on the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:26.82,Kingdom-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian, it seems the side that was hit was ours and the Yufeng Unit's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬さま\Nどうやら 当たったのは我々と―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉鳳隊のようですな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.29,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Prepare to leave at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつでも出られる準備をしておけ！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土門）ひるむな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.46,Kingdom-Main,Tu,0,0,0,,Do not falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:41.01,Kingdom-Main,Tu,0,0,0,,Now's the time to show them the fury of the Great State of Qin Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:40.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大秦国軍の恐ろしさ\N今こそ見せてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:47.69,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin! The battle on the right seems quite intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの 右の戦闘が激しいようです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.25,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Do you think Lun Hu could be on the right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 輪虎は右翼に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは違う\N（楚水）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.96,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日の輪虎は 本気で来る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:55.77,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Today, Lun Hu is going to attack seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつが出たら\N絶対あんなもんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Once he gets going, you can bet it's not gonna be anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.54,Kingdom-Thought,Rong,0,0,0,,The enemy's inner-ranks have started moving... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥の敵が 移動を始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:17.80,Kingdom-Thought,Rong,0,0,0,,The right-wing enemy is turning in... the opposite direction?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右翼の敵は 逆方向に旋回している
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:22.40,Kingdom-Thought,Rong,0,0,0,,What... What is going on here?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:22.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ 何が起こっているのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:30.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?! There's a huge dust cloud rising over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）何だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N前に すごい砂煙が上がっているぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫(かくきょう)）蒙驁将軍 あ… あれを！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:33.19,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Men Ao, o-over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巨大な渦が２つ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There are two giant vortexes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:54.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're... gradually moving forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）ゆっくり 前に進んでる…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）“輪動(りんどう)”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.84,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Wheel movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:05.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしもウワサでしか聞いておらぬが\Nかつて 輪虎は―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:05.37,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I had only heard rumors of it, but supposedly Lun Hu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪動という特異な戦術で―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:13.48,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,penetrated Wang Qi of the Six Great Generals' defense unit using a wheel movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:13.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの六大将軍 王騎(おうき)の守備を\N貫いたといわれておる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:19.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええい！ 何か仕掛けてくるぞ！\N左右の軍に厚みを作れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.03,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,They're going to try something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.40,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,Thicken defenses in the right and left armies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近１）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Rong Bei's reaction was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）栄備将軍の対応も早い！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）\N渦の前に兵を送って 分厚くした！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:29.50,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He sent soldiers to the front of the vortexes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\Nウワーッ！ ヤツらを止めろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.01,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.01,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Their momentum is too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）この勢いはムリだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:53.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンンッ… こ… これが輪動の正体か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:53.71,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,S-So this is the true form of the wheel movement? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:57.60,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,With the two vortexes spinning in opposite directions, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:10:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに 逆方向に回転する渦は\N横陣の力を左右に分けてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.56,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,they separate the horizontal formation's strength to the left and the right. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして そこに生じた隙間に―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.99,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,And in the opening that creates... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:07.78,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,the end of the wheel breaks into the defense in a pyramid shape! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪動の先端が\Nキリのように突入していく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:12.00,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,Oh no. The target of that wheel movement is... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:12.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いかん　あの輪動の攻撃の的は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.04,Kingdom-Thought,Meng,0,0,0,,Rong Bei's formation! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,栄備の陣じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.50,Kingdom-Main,Rong,0,0,0,,They failed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しくじったか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.05,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,Lord Ben! There's a change at the left wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賁さま！ 左翼で異変が！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.01,Kingdom-Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Lord Meng Tian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.01,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit's station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊の持ち場か…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.83,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊長！\N（信）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:29.56,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.69,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:01.72,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs70\be0.5\pos(987.047,317.343)}Lun Hu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.79,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,What a fighting style...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:11.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏良）なんという戦い方だ\Nついていくだけで兵の体力が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.85,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,Just keeping up with him is taking all of our soldier's stamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\Nこれほどの突破劇も初めてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.48,Kingdom-Thought,Wei,0,0,0,,But I've never felt such a vehement charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.39,Kingdom-Main,Wei,0,0,0,,Do not falter, State of Wei soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひるむな魏国兵！ ここが正念場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.98,Kingdom-Main,Wei,0,0,0,,This is do-or-die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:28.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（側近１）く… 来るぞ！ 守れ！\N（側近２）将軍 お下がりを！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.74,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,H-Here they come, defend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.99,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍 お早く！\N（側近２）栄備将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Rong Bei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（栄備）ンンッ… ハアッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:41.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎め… どうやら格が違ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:41.25,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Lun Hu... It looks like we're not in the same league. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:45.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せがれほどの若者に\Nあとを託さねばならぬとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:45.35,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,I actually need a bunch of punk kids to have my back... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.97,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Even if I am no match for Lun Hu, I can at least get one strike in on him! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かなわぬまでも\Nせめて輪虎に ひと太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:12.75,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Please, my lord... I wish you good fortune in this war... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか 殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご武運を…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:20.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）ど… どうなった？\N栄備将軍の旗が消えたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.91,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Rong Bei's flag disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）ま… まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:21.79,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.24,Kingdom-Thought,Guy,0,0,0,,Rong Bei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,栄備…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:32.85,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,After losing a general, the State of Qin soldiers will be paralyzed. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:32.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将を失ったせいで\N秦国兵の統制はマヒしている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.31,Kingdom-Thought,Lun,0,0,0,,Now to charge straight to the headquarters. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは 一気に本陣を突くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（郭叫）マ… マズイぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,His momentum brought him all the way through the horizontal unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの勢いで横陣を突破されたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:45.05,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Now the only thing between him and this headquarters is a few reserve units!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは この本陣との間には\N僅かな予備隊しかいない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.59,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎… ンッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go, you bastards! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし 行くぞ てめえら！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:03.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝者）待て 飛信隊！\N全兵で動いてはならん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wait, Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We can't have all soldiers moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Why, old messenger guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんでだよ？ 伝者のおっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.68,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,With this enemy right in front of us, we'll still need some on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:10.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この正面の敵で\Nまだ待機している軍がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:14.26,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, leave 200 here before you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念のための予備として\N200は ここに置いていくんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.22,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.66,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,The natural thing to do would be to attack with all of our soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全兵をもって当たるのが\N当然であろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならん！ 命令だ！\N（信）クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No! This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渕さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:30.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:33.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hurry and pick 200 men from the heavily injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:33.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急いで\Nケガの重いヤツから200人集めろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.62,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Ah, yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ あっ はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:40.76,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei, I'm leaving leadership of the people here to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:40.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N羌瘣(きょうかい) ここの指揮 お前に任せるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.13,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,He's leaving Lord Qiang Lei?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣どのを置いていく？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか ケガをしているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.13,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,Could he... be injured? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）\Nやはり 輪虎兵に囲まれたときに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.30,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,It must've been when we were surrounded by Lun Hu soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:54.14,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,It's pointless to be fussing over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）妙な気遣いは無用だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなんじゃねえ　今日の戦いは\N何が起こるか分からねえから―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:59.23,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I don't know what's gonna happen in today's fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,200の指揮をお前に頼むんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.60,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,so that's why I'm asking you to lead 200!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:06.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Remember, I've gotten plenty of protection from {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに お前の援護は十分もらった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:12.65,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また あとでな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.38,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:16.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's go, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ てめえら！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）止めろー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:36.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏良）よ～し！\Nもはや敵に我らを止めるすべはない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.94,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.79,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy has no way of stopping us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:39.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁本陣まで一気に攻め落とすぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.56,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Keep mowing them down until we make it to Meng Ao's headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:53.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You've lost, State of Qin dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国の犬ども！ 貴様らの負けだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.98,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊長に続けー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.24,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Follow after the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）あっ… 将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:54.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy has stopped moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）敵の足が止まった…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:08.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're not getting away again. I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:08.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう逃げねえし 逃がさねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.55,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's time to settle this, Lun Hu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決着の時だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Vice Captain Qiang Lei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:33.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N羌瘣副長… 大丈夫ですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:35.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Are the captain and the others... going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊長たちは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.28,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:50.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚いたな　その右腕\N当分 使えないと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.39,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I thought you wouldn't be able to use that right arm for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.59,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,This guy, with one hand, he's... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつ 片手で…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.90,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Looks like you can't use your left arm anymore, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）てめえの左腕は\N使い物にならなくなったようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:05.42,Kingdom-Main,Qu,0,0,0,,Xin! The left! Go for his left side with his crippled hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（去亥(きょがい)）信！ 左だ！\N手が使えない左に回り込め！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言われなくても分かってらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.58,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,It's impossible. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:12.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムリだ… 輪虎は 巧みな馬術で\N回らせないようにしている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.92,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,Lun Hu will use his deft horse-riding skills to turn that side away from him. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:18.60,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,And despite the fact that his left hand was mutilated yesterday, he's still fighting coolly. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも 昨日\N左手をやられたにもかかわらず―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平然と戦っている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:25.43,Kingdom-Thought,Chu,0,0,0,,Under Lian Po, this man really must have survived scenes of carnage that we can't even imagine. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり ヤツは廉頗のもとで―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の想像を絶する修羅場を\Nくぐり抜けてきたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.94,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Xin... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李充(りじゅう)）あっ…\N殿 後ろが どうかされましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.17,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is something happening behind us? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う～む…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.56,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに！ こいつ 昨日より…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.79,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Is this guy even stronger than before...?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:50.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:51.96,Kingdom-Main,,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:51.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.96,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,You'd best not make the mistake of thinking I'll be weaker today than I was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:57.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が昨日より弱っているなんて\N勘違いしちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:03.84,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,I've got tons of experience of only being able to fight with one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,片手が使えない戦いなんて\Nいくらでも経験してきたし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:08.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何より\N今日は このあと約束があるんでね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:08.35,Kingdom-Main,Lun,0,0,0,,But most of all, I have a "promise" to fulfill after this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.81,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵１）\N正面 盛り上がってんな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:19.71,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Sounds like things are really heating up at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう やっぱ外れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Man, we really got the short straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろの見張りなんて\Nずっと山見てるだけだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All you get to do as the rear guard is to stare at mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵２）バカ 真面目にやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You idiot, get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:32.24,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The back of this headquarters is comparatively less steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:32.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この本陣 後ろは比較的 傾斜が緩い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:38.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,If you're the enemy, your only choices are to force your way through the front or go around to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵にすれば\N正面を強行突破するか―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろに回り込むしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.38,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But you can't send a large army to the back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵１）だが\N後ろに 大軍は送り込めないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:45.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No. They could definitely pull off a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:45.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 奇襲攻撃程度なら\N十分 展開できる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かっ… そんなんで\N本陣が落とせるかよ　ムダムダ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:50.39,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No way, man. The headquarters could never fall to something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:57.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ア～ッ… 正面の戦い 見物してえよ\N実際に戦うのはイヤだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:55.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I wanna see the battle in the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.91,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Not that I wanna actually fight, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい\N（守備兵１）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:58.86,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？\N（守備兵２）何だ？ あれは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.78,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 騎馬 …だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's a... mounted soldier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:10.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,て… 敵か？\N（守備兵１）さあ… でも１騎だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.79,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Dunno. But it's just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Who is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:13.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（守備兵２）何だ？ あいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:46.03,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Hey, Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）こら 蒙驁！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:51.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっぴり腰が直ったか\N廉頗さまが見に来てやったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.40,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Have you gotten over your weak nerve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:51.91,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Lord Lian Po is here to see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.24,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Did he say Lian Po?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗だと！\N（守備兵）バカな！ 本物か？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.91,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No way, is that really him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I definitely felt a sense of intimidation from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:01.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし あの威圧感は確かに…\N（守備兵）ウワサ以上の大男だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He's even bigger than the rumors said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:02.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ こんな所に１人で！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Why is he at a place like this alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:11.57,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,M-My lord, is that truly Lian Po?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:11.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬令）と… 殿\Nあれは まさしく廉頗では？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:18.44,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,Lian Po... You remembered me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,廉頗…\N覚えておったのか わしのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:23.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと下りてこい！\N一騎打ちでカタをつけるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.08,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Hurry and get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.44,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,We'll settle this one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ！ い… 一騎打ち？\N（守備兵）本気で言っているのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,O-One on one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.03,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is he being serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの\N蒙驁さまが受けるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There's no way Lord Meng Ao would accept something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:34.91,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,We did it plenty of times in the past, didn't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）\N確か 昔 何度かやったであろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ！\N貴様が小便漏らして逃げ出した―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.96,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure you always pissed yourself and turned tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:43.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの続きをやろうと\N言っておるのじゃ　来い 蒙驁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:41.71,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I'm saying we continue that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.55,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Come, Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:47.88,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I don't mind fighting empty handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちは素手でも かまわんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.33,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.85,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,The way he teases people hasn't changed a bit. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の おちょくり方も\N変わっておらぬわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.89,Kingdom-Thought,Ao,0,0,0,,But I'm actually quite happy with this. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それは それで うれしいわい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.18,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）よし 始めるぞ！\N（馬令）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:02.90,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,配置に就け！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Call every soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）全兵を呼べ！ 急げ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.90,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:14.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノリ悪し ハハハハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.53,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Looks like he's not game for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.41,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おい あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:39.09,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Okay, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ～て やるかい
